The key part is `tb.tokeniser.transition(TokeniserState.Rcdata);` and `tb.transition(Text);` - this puts both the tokeniser AND the tree builder into special modes.

When the tokeniser is in Rcdata mode, it only comes out when it sees the proper closing tag. But the TreeBuilder is in Text mode, and maybe the issue is that Text mode should be more responsive to start tags.

